            <title>[CASSANDRA-16412] nodetool status doesn&apos;t work without system_traces</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16412</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Error: The node does not have system_traces yet, probably still bootstrapping&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s no reason we can&apos;t show status because of this, we can simply log that the effective ownership is unknown, like we used to, rather than forcing a user to go to another machine to find out what&apos;s going on in the ring.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
