                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17273881" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 28 Jan 2021 17:22:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also note that when system_traces does exist, the effective ownership is still unknown and displayed as &apos;?&apos;, so this delay is pointless.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17283057" author="edimitrova" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2021 14:50:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good news &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=brandon.williams&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;brandon.williams&quot;&gt;brandon.williams&lt;/a&gt;&#160;, I think what you mentioned is already fixed actually as part of&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16283&quot; title=&quot;Incorrect output in &amp;quot;nodetool status -r&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-16283&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-16283&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, it was a week or two ago &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17283061" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2021 14:54:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah, yes.  Well at least that much is fixed here &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17283063" author="edimitrova" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2021 14:56:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, Indeed, that looked ugly &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17284663" author="bereng" created="Mon, 15 Feb 2021 10:57:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi quick q to see if iiuc. Are you guys suggesting?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;./nodetool status

Error: The node does not have system_traces yet, probably still bootstrapping
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should instead be?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;./nodetool status
Datacenter: datacenter1
=======================
Status=Up/Down
|/ State=Normal/Leaving/Joining/Moving
--  Address    Load       Tokens  Owns  Host ID                               Rack 
UN  127.0.0.1  79.49 KiB  16      ?     39a22b2d-cd2e-41cc-b613-53ba78b6564b  rack1

Note: Unkown ownership as we&apos;re still bootstrapping.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17286560" author="brandon.williams" created="Thu, 18 Feb 2021 15:59:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I don&apos;t want to throw the baby out with the bathwater just because we don&apos;t know the ownership; there&apos;s plenty of other useful information.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17287015" author="bereng" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2021 11:39:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Up for review iiuc what was being asked.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17287376" author="brandon.williams" created="Fri, 19 Feb 2021 21:38:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed, thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
